{"tree":{"type":"node","kind":"SOURCE_FILE","width":34,"children":[{"type":"node","kind":"LET_BINDING","width":34,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"let","width":3},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"IDENT_PATTERN","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"x","width":1}]},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"=","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":"\n  ","width":3},{"type":"node","kind":"LET_EXPR","width":24,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"let","width":3},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"ERROR","width":6,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"module","width":6}]},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"INFIX_EXPR","width":4,"children":[{"type":"node","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"M","width":1}]},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"=","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"N","width":1}]}]},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"in","width":2},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":"\n  ","width":3},{"type":"node","kind":"FIELD_ACCESS_EXPR","width":4,"children":[{"type":"node","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"M","width":1}]},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":".","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"f","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":"\n","width":1}]}]}]}]},"diagnostics":[{"kind":{"id":"E0007","name":"invalid-pattern","expected":"identifier or pattern","found":{"kind":"keyword","text":"module"},"fix":"use a different name like module_","hint":"\nThe left side of a let-expression allows you to pattern match on values to assign them to variables, but also to deconstruct them and access their inner values.\n\n   ```ocaml\n   let variable = 42 in\n   let { x; _ } = point in\n   let Some x = optional in\n   (* ... *)\n   ```\n\nBeware that pattern matching on only one of many possible values will lead to runtime errors!\n"},"span":{"start":20,"end":21}},{"kind":{"id":"E0003","name":"missing-let-binding-equals","expected":"=","found":{"kind":"identifier","text":"M"},"fix":"add = between the pattern and expression","hint":"Every let binding needs an = between the pattern and the expression."},"span":{"start":20,"end":20}}]}
